Package hr.fer.zemris.java.hw11.jnotepadpp.elements.actions

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChangeCaseAction
    Case editing action for use with Notepad implementing classes.
    CloseAction
    Localizable action that closes the editor of the given Notepad using JTabbedPane as it's content pane.
    CloseAllAction
    Localizable action that closes all editors of the given Notepad using JTabbedPane as it's content pane.
    CopyAction
    Localizable action that copies from the current editor of the Notepad into the clipboar.
    CutAction
    Localizable action that cuts from the current editor of the Notepad into the clipboar.
    DeleteAction
    Localizable action that deletes from the current editor of the Notepad.
    ExitAction
    Localizable action that calls the exit() method of the Notepad.
    InvertCaseAction
    Invert case action of the Notepad.
    LanguageSelectAction
    Language select action of the implementing Notepad.
    NewFileAction
    Localizable action that calls the newEditor() method of the Notepad.
    OpenAction
    Localizable action that tries to open a file and call setEditor() and setPath() methods of the Notepad.
    PasteAction
    Localizable action that copies from the current editor of the Notepad into the clipboar.
    SaveAction
    Localizable action that tries to save a file and call setFilePath() method of the Notepad.
    SaveAsAction
    Localizable action that tries to save a file and call setFilePath() method of the Notepad.
    SelectAllAction
    Localizable action that selects all text from the current editor of the Notepad.
    SortAction
    Parent action of Notepad actions used for sorting editor lines.
    SortAscendingAction
    Sort action of the Notepad that sorts the selected lines in ascending order.
    SortDescendingAction
    Sort action of the Notepad that sorts the selected lines in descending order.
    StatisticsAction
    Statistics showing action of the Notepad.
    ToLowerCaseAction
    To lower case action of the Notepad.
    ToUpperCaseAction
    To upper case action of the Notepad.
    UniqueAction
    Sort action of the Notepad that removes duplicated from the selected lines.
